HEADWORD: Princedom
<hw>Prince"dom</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The jurisdiction,
sovereignty, rank, or estate of a prince.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thrones, <qex>princedoms</qex>, powers, dominions, I reduce.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Princehood</ent>⟦br⟧
